<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="義解" xml:id="gsz0745c20shiXiYuan"><lb
n="0745c20" ed="T"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0745c20"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000013213">越州應天山寺</placeName><persName key="A009838">希圓</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0745c21"/><persName key="A009838">釋希圓</persName>，姓張氏，<placeName key="PL000000009928">姑蘇</placeName>人也。宗親豪富，而獨捨<lb
ed="T" n="0745c22"/>家，從登戒法，便遊講肆。不滯一方，勤修<lb
ed="T" n="0745c23"/>三學<ptr type="glossary" target="#g182"/>，良深歲稔，尤至博通，時推俊邁，因命<lb
ed="T" n="0745c24"/>講訓。<date notBefore-iso="+0885-04-06" key="j20443962045496" notAfter-iso="+0888-04-10"><name>光啟</name>中</date>，屬<persName key="A009840">徐約</persName>軍亂<ptr target="#n140"/>，<persName key="A009841">孫儒</persName>略地，<placeName key="PL000000008352">吳苑</placeName>俶<lb
ed="T" n="0745c25"/>擾<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1048"/>。<persName key="A009838">圓</persName>由<placeName key="PL000000009882">通玄寺</placeName>附商船，避地于<placeName key="PL000000013798">甬東</placeName>。其估<lb
ed="T" n="0745c26"/>客偕<placeName key="PL000000013239">越</placeName>人也，篤重於<persName key="A009838">圓</persName>，召居<placeName key="PL000000013213">會稽寶林山<lb
ed="T" n="0745c27"/>寺</placeName>。形雖ㄠ<anchor xml:id="beg0745005"/>麼<anchor xml:id="end0745005"/><ptr type="glossary" target="#g726"/>，性且強幹，與時寡合，多事宴<lb
ed="T" n="0745c28"/>默<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1049"/>。或問<ref type="person" target="#A009838">之</ref>，則曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A009838">吾</ref>逍遙乎無形之場，同師<lb
ed="T" n="0745c29"/>子遊戲耳。」<date notBefore-iso="+0892-02-26" key="j20469132047631" notAfter-iso="+0894-02-13"><name>景福</name>中</date>，於<ref type="place" target="#PL000000013213">山寺</ref>演暢經論，同聲<pb ed="T" n="0746a" xml:id="T50.2061.0746a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0746a01"/>相應，求法者至。乃著《玄中鈔》數卷，皆當義妙<lb
ed="T" n="0746a02"/>辭也。恒勸人急修上生之業，且曰：「非知之<lb
ed="T" n="0746a03"/>難，行之為難。汝曹勉旃<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1050"/>。」<persName key="A009838">圓</persName>六時<ptr type="glossary" target="#g178"/><anchor xml:id="beg0746sgsz1"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0746sgsz1"/>懺，未嘗<lb
ed="T" n="0746a04"/>少缺。居小房，即<placeName key="PL000000013214">瑯瑘山</placeName>頂，是山也，傳云從<lb
ed="T" n="0746a05"/><placeName key="PL000000020564">瑯瑘臺</placeName>飛來，<anchor xml:id="beg0746sgsz2"/>此<anchor xml:id="end0746sgsz2"/>處先是屠坊，故皆鎮于其<lb
ed="T" n="0746a06"/>下。<ref type="place" target="#PL000000013214">山</ref>之<anchor xml:id="beg0746001"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>家</sic><corr>冡</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0746001"/>有井，井有鰻鯠焉，水有<anchor xml:id="beg0746002"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>應</sic><corr>盈</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0746002"/><lb
ed="T" n="0746a07"/>縮，應大江之潮候，甚多靈怪。一云此處<persName key="A002761">禹</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0746a08"/>鎖<placeName key="PL000000008367">浙江</placeName>蛟蜃之屬，其名曰蛆。蛆有雙耳，其<lb
ed="T" n="0746a09"/>色蒼黃，或緣竹木，必風雨至矣。今或出石<lb
ed="T" n="0746a10"/>竅，入僧居溝渠中，見人不驚，握則跳梁如<lb
ed="T" n="0746a11"/>怒狀。唯<anchor xml:id="beg0746003"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>徧</sic><corr>偏</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0746003"/>入<persName key="A009838">圓</persName>房，<persName key="A009838">圓</persName>手執宛轉屑就，乃為<lb
ed="T" n="0746a12"/>之受歸戒，令勿作風雹之妖。暨<persName key="A009838">圓</persName>終，而多<lb
ed="T" n="0746a13"/>暴風雨也。<persName key="A009838">圓</persName>之修習，願見<persName key="A001428">彌勒</persName>。一日講次，<lb
ed="T" n="0746a14"/>屹然坐終于法座，時眾聞異香<anchor xml:id="beg0746sgsz3"/>裛<anchor xml:id="end0746sgsz3"/>孴<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1051"/>，天樂錚<lb
ed="T" n="0746a15"/>鏦，或絕或連，七日後已，此真上生<ptr target="#n1052"/>之證歟！則<lb
ed="T" n="0746a16"/><date from-iso="+0895-05-03" key="j20480752048103" to-iso="+0895-05-31"><name>乾寧</name>二年四月</date>也。還山之日，僧眾置祭于寺<lb
ed="T" n="0746a17"/>門。無何<ptr type="glossary" target="#g493"/>，有人茜<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1053"/>袍象笏拜跪愴然。𢠵怳<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1054"/>之間，<lb
ed="T" n="0746a18"/>杳無蹤迹，眾莫能測焉。<anchor xml:id="beg0746004"/>荼<anchor xml:id="end0746004"/>毘，收舍利七百<lb
ed="T" n="0746a19"/>餘粒，被<placeName key="PL000000012470">四明</placeName>人齎往<placeName key="PL000000048606">新羅國</placeName>矣。</p>
